display_long_description:
Run, Jump, Bounce and Climb in the exciting world of Orangu! In Orangu, you are a species of monkey that we completely made up! Explore the Orangu facility and meet other Orangus!

When you enter Orangu, you are spawned into the control room. On the computer, you can join rooms, or customise your name, player colour and settings. Once you leave the control room, you have many options of places to go to, you could either go into the maps tunnel, or the shop tunnel!

Explore the dense forest, the cove, the hoverpark, the crystal caves or the zer gravity zone! There is a lot to do in these maps so explore!

Customise your Orangu in the shop! For every day you play, you gain 100 currency to spend on cosmetics, these cosmetics include ones for your head, hands, face, and body! Some cosmetics are limited however and may leave the shop soon!

So are you ready to explore the world of Orangu? I hope the answer is yes! See you in the facility!
